skills.description:
For 5s, beams of light rain down, randomly striking enemies in a massive circular area, dealing physical damage equal to 140% of Attack up to 5 times per second. Each target can only be hit once every 0.5s. If cast while under [Grace], removes the status and gains additional effects based on the number of [Radiant Ember] stacks:
1: Upon casting, grants a Shield equal to 150% of Attack for 6s, and allies in the area gain [Attack Boost];
2: Increases damage by 40%, and grants 4 stacks of [Deathrattle] when the skill ends;
3: Upon casting, all allies except self gain [Attack Boost], while self gains [Significant Attack Boost];
